article_metadata.description: She’s off to see the wizard … The AP says: “Ruth Robinson Duccini, the last of the original female Munchkins from the 1939 movie 'The Wizard of Oz,' has died. She was 95. With her death, only one actor who played one of the original 124 Munchkins in the movie remains alive.

og.title: Minnesota Munchkin passes away at 95
